version.author: LKC
version.changelog: + Fixed right click jumping behaviour + Added toolbar icon: LKC - Content Navigator.png * v0.8beta (2022-01-12) + Fixed expanding and collapsing when no selection + Fixed deselection issues + Fixed various unwanted ALT + Right Click results * v0.7beta (2022-01-11) + Standalone license support + Added support for multi selection (using CTRL/SHIFT + Click) + Added support for jump modifier (using ALT + Click) + Added support for quick expand (using ALT + Right Click) + Added support for quick collapse (using ALT + SHIFT + Right Click) + Added support for FREE version (up to 3 depth levels and 20 list items)

version.author: LKC
version.changelog: + Added search box (premium feature) with multi term support (comma is a term separator) + Added support for always hidden tracks (any track with ## in its name) + Added support to rename tracks from Content Navigator (ALT + Double Click) + Added 'Solo' in Navigation Options + Improved stability of the tool (added crash safety)

version.author: LKC
version.changelog: + Fixed issue in search box with special characters like (^$()%.[]*+-?)

version.author: LKC
version.changelog: + Improved anti-crash security for multi-selection + Added support for coloring tracks using third-party scripts like ReaNoir or Colour Swatch + License management improvement * v1.03beta (2022-04-19) + Fixed issue with folder selection when using CTRL+Left Click or SHIFT+Left Click
